138_"/><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-139_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-141_">A practical braided look with the wow factor. Once you’ve mastered the execution of a fishtail, you’ll be sure to impress the other mums at home time. Although a fishtail braid may look daunting at first, they’re a surprisingly easy hairstyle to construct with a little practice. Not only are they stunning, when finished correctly they can hold perfectly all day, whatever your child throws at you! Check out our <a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/how-to-create-easy-fishtail-braid-with-cliphair" target="_blank">Easy Fishtail Braid Tutorial</a> to ensure you get the perfect braid every time.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-142_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-brSvTw iyWbaU pf-143_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" id="pixie" class="sc-hOGkXu eBgidd pf-144_"><a data-link="inherit" href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/mum-hair-care-easy-hairstyles-for-new-mum#index" target="_self"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-146_">Try Extremely Low Maintenance Hair with the Pixie</span></a></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-371066da--Mum-hair-pixie_500x.jpg?v=1629107585" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-371066da--Mum-hair-pixie.jpg?v=1629107585 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-371066da--Mum-hair-pixie_500x.jpg?v=1629107585 320w" width="835" height="626" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy" alt="Pixie cut" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jQrDum igoalK pf-147_"/><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-148_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-150_">If short hair is easy to maintain, pixie hair is the master of easy hairstyles. If you’re brave enough to chop it all off, try a pixie haircut! Undeniably short, spiky, and super cute, the pixie is one for the bold. But, as a new mum you’re as bold as they come, right? The beauty of the pixie hair cut is they work for just about any type of hair or face shape. They’re also a go to for mums with messy ones as the absence of long tresses mean your locks will stay CLEAN. This simple and easy hairstyle is incredibly fashionable for 2021 (who says mums can’t stay on trend), makes a statement and is perfect for mothers who are short on time. Isn’t that all of you?</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-151_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-brSvTw iyWbaU pf-152_"><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-153_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-brSvTw iyWbaU pf-154_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" id="lob" class="sc-hOGkXu eBgidd pf-155_"><a data-link="inherit" href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/mum-hair-care-easy-hairstyles-for-new-mum#index" target="_self"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-157_">Forget Mum Bobs, Try Feminine Lobs</span></a></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-1066da7b--Mum-hair-lob_500x.jpg?v=1629107638" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-1066da7b--Mum-hair-lob.jpg?v=1629107638 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-1066da7b--Mum-hair-lob_500x.jpg?v=1629107638 320w" width="835" height="626" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy" alt="Feminine Lobs" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jQrDum igoalK pf-158_"/><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-159_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-161_">Who say’s mum hair has to be short? Forget the bobs and pixies, you don’t have to cut off your locks just because you have kids. Keep your precious tresses and revitalize your femininity with a long bob, or lob as it’s ingeniously named. Lobs were in in 2019, 2020… even 2021! The fact is this simple and easy hairstyle rarely goes out of fashion, and it’s a go to for new mums who want to break away from the mum hair stereotype. Embrace this easy hairstyle from day to night, if you’d like to add some extra curls to your lob, make sure to stock up on a curl defining crème to keep your lob looking perfectly wavy whatever the time.</span></p></div></div></div><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" id="summary" class="sc-hOGkXu eBgidd pf-162_"><a data-link="inherit" href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/mum-hair-care-easy-hairstyles-for-new-mum#index" target="_self"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-164_">Mum Hair: Summary</span></a></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-66da7bda--Mum-hair_500x.jpg?v=1629107685" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-66da7bda--Mum-hair.jpg?v=1629107685 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-66da7bda--Mum-hair_500x.jpg?v=1629107685 320w" width="835" height="626" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy" alt="Mum summary" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jQrDum igoalK pf-165_"/><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-166_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-168_">Does becoming a mum mean you have to sacrifice your style? Hell no! We hope this list of simple and easy hairstyles for new mum has given you some major hair inspo. At the end of the day, mums can rock any hair style they want! Just be prepared for some extra early mornings if you want to go ful